OL,3,C'Dangerous' Somerset man murdered
OL,4,Cgirlfriend and plied female victims
OL,5,Cwith drugs
OL,7,FA man has been found guilty of
OL,8,Fmurdering his girlfriend in Frome, on
OL,9,Fthe night she planned to end their
OL,10,Frelationship.
OL,12,FKieron Goodwin, 33, fatally strangled
OL,13,FOlivia Wood, 29, on 30 July 2024 -
OL,14,Fafter she was subjected to months of
OL,15,Fabuse.
OL,17,FHe has also been found guilty of 15
OL,18,Fother offences committed against
OL,19,FOlivia and three other women over a
OL,20,Ffive-year period.
