OL,7,FOlivia had also transferred Goodwin
OL,8,Fmore than #6,000 to help him pay his
OL,9,Fbills, which he ultimately spent on
OL,10,Fcocaine.
OL,12,FAt 2.50am on Tuesday 30 July 2024,
OL,13,FGoodwin made a 999 call to the
OL,14,Fambulance service reporting that
OL,15,FOlivia was not breathing, and she was
OL,16,Ftaken to hospital where she later died.
OL,18,FPolice officers later arrived to his
OL,19,Fflat in Portway, after paramedics
